The paper discusses the performance of a machine learning algorithm (GBDT) in a distributed setting, which falls under the category of large-scale data processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DB (Databases), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
